bsolute intervals (1.6-2.7)Mpc and\n(0.7-1.7)kpc, respectively, depending on the redshift and on the seeing. This\nallows the planned studies to get a valuable description of the local\nproperties of clusters and galaxies in clusters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 Jul 2005 10:54:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 4 Oct 2005 09:10:04 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 5 Oct 2005 13:40:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
