e comparisons with\nexperiment require better understanding of the microscopic basis of the\nphenomenological model parameters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 Jul 2005 14:53:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 17 Jan 2006 19:36:08 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 18 Jan 2006 22:54:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-01-31"}
